It’s ~bin~ quite the month with the one they call “Margaret” over here. Mags, you’re a helluva patient and roomie—I’ll split a hasselback potato with you anytime, but you’re banned from button services for a while. I hate to leave, but I’m heading back to Chicago with my new motto in mind: good leg to heaven, bad leg to hell! Here’s hoping you can ditch those sticks soon so you can just do a quick whizz around. And yes, I’ll get you another water. Xx Cheeky Chipmunk 🐿👭#thaaankYOU! #SILENCE
